| PROMOTIONS | TOTAL | CAST(PROMOTIONSASDECIMAL(15,4))/CAST(TOTALASDECIMAL(15,4))*100 |
+------------+-------+----------------------------------------------------------------+
|       NULL |  NULL |                                                           NULL |
